quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  21,91,"[JaŇčto kadi fii] oya [cuddii…óo] deennoo…óo farju makko on Min wutti e makko immorde e Fittaandu amen, Min mba…ói mo kaŇčko e ge…óaljo makko on Ma'ande wona nde winndere nden."
  21,92,"Pellet, …óee mofte mo'on ko mofte go'ote, ko Min ngoni Joomi mo'on Rewee Lam."
  21,93,"∆Āe ta∆īi fiyaake ma…ď…ďe on hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, …ďe fof ko fa'ade ka am …ďe nduttoytoo."
  21,94,"Kala gollu…óo immorde e mo∆ī∆īu…ói …óin hara kaŇčko ko o gooŇč…óin…óo, dullugol alaa fii golle makko …óen, pellet, Minen Min mbinndanay mo."
  21,95,"No harmani saare nde Mon kalki …óum, won'de kam…ďe …ďe mduttataako [ton]."
  21,96,"Haa si udditoyaama Ya'ajuuja e Ma'ajuuja, hara kam…ďe immorde e kala na…óel he…ďe cortoo."
  21,97,"Fodoore Goongaare nde …ďadike, tawi kayre puttini gii…óe …ďen yeddu…ďe, […ďe mbi'a:] "Eeyoo bone amen, gooŇč…óii min laatinoke e nder welsindaare immorde e …óu'um, ko woni, men laatike too√Ī…ďe."
  21,98,"Pellet, onon e ko ndewoton kon ga Alla, ko on doccote Jahannama. Onon, ko on joloyay…ďe e magge."
  21,99,"Sinndo …ďee laatinoke rewetee…ďe …ďe njolataano e magge. ∆Āe fof ma…ď…ďe ko …ďe luttintee…ďe e ndeer magge."
  21,100,"No woodani …ďe e ndeer magge haraango, kam…ďe …ďe nanataa ndeer ton."
  21,101,"Pellet, …ďeen …ďe mo∆ī∆īi …ói adanii …óum immorde ka amen …ďeen …óoon ko …ďe wo…ó…óintintee…ďe ga magge."